Great accomplishment seems unfinished But its use is continuous. Great
 fullness seems empty But in use is inexhaustible.
Great straightness seems bent, Great skill seems clumsy, Great eloquence
 seems mute.
Exertion overcomes cold. Calm overcomes heat. Pure calm is the norm under
 heaven.
